title: Full Stack
text: I have worked for a variety of companies across multiple industries. With each of these companies, I have played an expansive full-stack role encompassing things such as making user friendly interfaces, creating efficient backends and apis, setting up pipelines for CI/CD, managing deployments of production ready code, and much more.
moretext: I have worked for a variety of company styles, from Enterprise companies to Startups, across multiple industries: Defense Contracting, Healthcare, Food and Beverage, and Entertainment. With each of these companies, I have played an expansive full-stack role encompassing things such as making user friendly interfaces, creating efficient backends and apis, setting up pipelines for CI/CD, managing deployments of production ready code, and much more.
